JIT - Just In Time (DEVELOPMENT) (BROWSER)

    ng serge (JIT Mode) development

    main.bundle.js
        component (es5)
        css
        view (html)

    HTML => JS (JS represent the view)

production? end users browser spend time to convert 
           html to js

---

AOT - Ahead of Time {Production}

Build => production release => Apply AOT

> ng build --prod (AOT)

> ng build  (This is not AOT, JIT)

AOT => HTML => TypeScript => TSC => JS (ES5) => Main.bundle.js

main.bundle.js (production)
    css
    component [es5]
    view (js)